column5: Plenty of room for a surf rod in there!!!
Feel sorry for the lifeguard that has to do the head count at the end of their shift !
The expected coliform count makes me want to barf!!!!
What's the point of going to the beach to sit under a sea of umbrella advertising....  When you could go here?:                  You notice that this place is within walking distance to the ocean?

I betcha the washroom line ups would be just brutal !!! Or worse all those people would just say forget the lines...and just do there business in the surf.....nice. Blue water Saturday morning...warm yellow water by Sunday afternoon.
boy that looks like fun! lol   thats more people than i ever care to see.  jason
